################################### pokemon router ############################


### GET one pokemon by id
GET {{api}}/pokemon/2





### GET one pokemon by name (not case sensitive nor accent sensitive)
GET {{local}}/pokemon/pikachu

### get all pokemon imunise
GET {{local}}/pokemon/imune/type/3

###get akk resistants pokemons 
GET {{api}}/pokemon/resist/type/1

###GET resistant and imune pokemon from a type
GET  {{api}}/pokemon/resist/imune/type/2
### GET all pokemon
GET {{api}}/pokemon/full-random

###GET pokemon by 2 types
GET {{api}}/pokemon/type/14/type/17

### GET all pokemon of one type
GET {{local}}/pokemon/type/30



### GET all pokemon by generation 
GET {{api}}/pokemon/gen/1



